Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.67,0:01:52.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110673,112675}Don't go this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.47,0:01:58.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:115470,118306}Crossing this river\Nis too dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:00.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119307,120850}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.68,0:02:06.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:124687,126689}Lassie!
