Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:19.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138826,139994}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.99,0:02:21.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139994,141496}It was just a bad dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.62,0:02:27.50,lassie episode,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:142622,147502}{\blur0.5\fad(300,0)\pos(320,295)}Welcome Back, Lassie
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.46,0:02:34.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152465,154133}{\i1}John.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:37.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:154133,157387}{\i1}There were no reports\Nof Lassie sightings today either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.38,0:02:42.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157387,162684}{\i1}She was last seen in\NWest Darlington, three days ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:48.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162684,168064}{\i1}But I strongly believe that Lassie is safe\Nand will arrive to your town soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:52.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170149,172068}Don't worry, Priscilla.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.06,0:02:56.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:172068,176781}Lassie is healthy\Nand she's on her way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.63,0:03:19.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193631,199011}I've been thinking about Lassie\Nall night long again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.11,0:03:39.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214110,219073}Even the results… from the laboratory…\Nsaid our chances aren't zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:39.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219073,219699}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:42.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219699,222577}We can do it.\NWe'll find that coal, Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:49.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:223786,229876}When I see these two working,\Ntheir enthusiasm kinda rubs off on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.37,0:03:51.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:230376,231169}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.16,0:03:54.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231169,234338}Alright! We won't lose to them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:55.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:234338,235465}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:07.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245641,247518}Ah? Sandy…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.51,0:04:08.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:247518,248436}How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.02,0:04:13.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251022,253566}I'm just hopeless…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:15.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253566,255318}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.31,0:04:16.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255318,256486}Here, a gift for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:19.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258654,259781}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.69,0:04:23.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260698,263534}Why am I always like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.53,0:04:26.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:263534,266746}Getting sick and all\Nwhen it matters the most.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.74,0:04:28.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266746,268414}I'm ashamed of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.41,0:04:30.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268414,270500}I can't help John at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.75,0:04:34.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270750,274545}I know how it's like.\NI feel the same, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.54,0:04:40.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274545,280176}All I can do is make tea\Nfor the miners when they're on a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:41.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280176,281219}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.21,0:04:46.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:281219,286057}John is working so hard,\Nhe's like an adult man…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.47,0:04:47.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286474,287141}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.14,0:04:52.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287141,292063}But Sandy, your sweets are very delicious.\NI'm sure everyone is happy to have them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:53.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292897,293815}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:55.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294899,295900}John…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:59.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:295900,299904}He must be dying\Nto go looking for Lassie,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:03.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299904,303825}and yet he's holding back\Nto do his best helping at the mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.57,0:05:08.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304575,308079}I'm sure he won't ever\Nlet her go again once she returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.29,0:05:15.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:311290,315878}I've always liked how Lassie and John\Nwere running around everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.92,0:05:21.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316921,321425}That sight always cheered me up\Nsomehow, and I wanted to join them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:25.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:323135,325304}I wish we could do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.01,0:05:28.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327014,328307}But what can we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:35.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334063,335731}All right, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.73,0:05:37.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:335731,337525}Time for your tea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.52,0:05:39.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337525,339569}Oh? What did you bring today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.98,0:05:42.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:339986,342196}Something to give you\Nenergy, a meat pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.57,0:05:45.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:342572,345741}I started to look forward\Nto this moment every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:46.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:345741,346951}All right, take a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:05:58.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358004,358880}How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.50,0:06:01.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:359505,361173}Yes, it was delicious. Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.59,0:06:06.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364594,366637}What? You already ate?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:14.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:373436,374604}John?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:15.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:374604,375771}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.77,0:06:18.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375771,378900}I can't help much here,\Nbut I do what I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.15,0:06:20.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379150,380568}"Can't help much"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:23.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:381360,383154}You're doing everything you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:27.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385865,387033}What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.78,0:06:29.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:387783,389035}A week?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:30.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389577,390786}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.78,0:06:34.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390786,394749}This is all I could get from him.\NWellington Coal Mine has reached its limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.74,0:06:39.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:394749,399128}The Duke said he won't be pumping\Nany more money into the mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.12,0:06:41.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:399128,401464}We did what we could,\Nand still haven't found the coal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:43.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:401464,403132}Maybe it really is time to give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:45.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:403132,405217}But a week? That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:46.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:405217,406761}Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:50.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406761,410514}We have to inform\Neveryone about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.51,0:06:54.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:410514,414101}We should give them as much time\Nas possible to let them make arrangements.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:59.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417188,419065}I haven't told John\Nabout any of this yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.56,0:07:03.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:420566,423527}Do you want me to tell him?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.52,0:07:06.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:423527,426280}I'm not sure if I can do it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.28,0:07:08.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426280,428574}No, I'm going to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.07,0:07:11.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:429075,431077}I think he'll understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:14.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:431077,434163}John has grown up a lot lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.62,0:07:15.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434622,435831}I hope you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:23.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440336,443589}What's the matter\Nwith the manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:27.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443589,447134}I heard he wants to tell us something\Nimportant. Doesn't happen very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:29.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:447134,449512}Finally, the end of the road, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:33.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:451722,453307}Hey, he's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.43,0:07:37.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455434,457061}Everyone, I'd like you to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.06,0:07:39.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457061,459355}The manager has\Nsomething to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:56.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:473703,476747}See? Strange, right? That rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:58.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:476747,478916}I extracted it from the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478916,480167}Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:02.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480167,482211}This is… I think that's…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:05.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:482503,485256}Can you bring me that book?\NThe one with the yellow cover.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.25,0:08:05.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:485256,485715}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:09.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486465,489427}Clean this place up\Nsometimes, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:10.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:489427,490136}This one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:13.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:490136,493222}No, the other one…\NThe third from the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493222,494849}Yes, this one! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:19.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:498519,499353}What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:21.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500855,501814}There!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:23.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501814,503566}There it is. An ammonite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:24.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:503858,504984}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.98,0:08:27.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:505985,507611}This is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:28.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:507611,508529}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:30.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508529,510072}This is huge, Sandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:36.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514535,516203}What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.12,0:08:39.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517121,519665}Sir, just tell us what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:42.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519665,522585}We're ready for everything\Nyou're going to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:49.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:526589,529508}Sir, should I speak\Nwith them instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:51.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:530342,531510}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:53.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531510,533179}The words just aren't coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538350,539310}Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.76,0:09:00.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:539769,540936}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.93,0:09:02.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540936,542188}Err…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.18,0:09:03.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:542188,543314}How to put it…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:06.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:544523,546317}What I wanted to say is…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.31,0:09:08.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546317,548527}You probably already know\Nwhat I'm about to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.52,0:09:10.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:548527,550404}Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:13.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:550404,553157}Sir, you need to hear this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:14.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553157,554408}It's serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:19.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:557203,559830}What's going on?\NWhy were you running?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.83,0:09:20.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559830,560998}Well, it's because…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.91,0:09:25.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:563918,565044}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.59,0:09:34.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573594,574470}What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:39.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:575387,579475}See? It's a critter from the same\Ngeological age as the coal in the mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.47,0:09:40.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579475,580684}It's called an ammonite.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:43.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:581393,583145}Which means…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:44.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:583145,584688}What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.68,0:09:48.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:584688,588734}The coal we mined came from\Nfossilized trees that had grown long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.19,0:09:51.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589193,591028}This clam comes from the—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:52.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591028,592029}It's not a clam!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:55.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592029,595741}Ammonites look a bit like clams,\Nbut they're entirely different organisms.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.82,0:10:01.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:597827,601831}In any case, this creature lived\Nin a time very close to the time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:03.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601831,603499}when the tree\Nthat made the coal grew.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.49,0:10:05.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:603499,605960}So it's possible we'll find\Nmore coal in the vicinity?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.96,0:10:07.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:605960,607878}Yes. It's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:11.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:608712,611132}All right! This is our mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.13,0:10:14.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611132,614176}No matter what anybody tells us,\Nwe've gotta dig! Dig as far as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:15.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614176,615094}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.09,0:10:16.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615094,616637}Ah, Colin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.63,0:10:18.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616637,618681}Hey, John… Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:20.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618681,620182}Thank you, Colin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.18,0:10:23.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620182,623602}I did nothing.\NIt was Sandy who discovered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.60,0:10:26.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623602,626272}But I thought\Nit was just a dumb rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:28.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626272,628065}Be proud of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.03,0:10:40.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:638033,640619}Hey! We found something more!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.61,0:10:41.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640619,641537}Is it coal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:44.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:641745,644206}No, it's another fossil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.20,0:10:45.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:644206,645040}It's a fossil, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:47.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645833,647251}What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:48.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:647251,648794}It looks huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:56.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654800,656760}What are your thoughts,\NProfessor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.76,0:11:01.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656760,661015}It is a great pleasure for the scientific world\Nto have a complete skeleton of Eryops,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.01,0:11:04.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661015,664018}which is considered one of\Nthe most important ancient relics.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.01,0:11:06.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664018,666979}We heard that the mine\Nis closing today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.97,0:11:09.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:666979,669565}In my previous geological survey\NI had established
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:12.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669565,672276}the possibility to find more coal\Nto be extremely slim.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:15.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672276,675529}I concluded at the time that\Na shutdown would be the best option,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.52,0:11:21.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675529,681535}but I would like to report to Duke Radling\Nthat it is no longer the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681535,683787}That is all. Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:25.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:683787,685581}Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.58,0:11:29.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685581,689376}No. You should thank the children.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:30.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:689376,690377}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.37,0:11:32.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690377,692129}Oh? Where's John, by the way?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:35.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692504,695758}He's at the bottom of the shaft\Nwith Mr. Beal and everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:37.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:695758,697259}He's done more than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.25,0:11:40.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697259,700137}He wants to continue\Nuntil the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.51,0:11:46.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705517,706435}John.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:47.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706435,707269}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:48.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707269,708395}You can stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.39,0:11:50.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708395,710064}I'll handle the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:50.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710064,710856}Okay, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:53.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:710856,713108}John! Get over here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:54.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713108,714735}What is it, Mr. Beal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.98,0:11:57.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:715986,717238}What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:05.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723619,725371}We've finally done it, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.12,0:12:10.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:728123,730125}We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.12,0:12:11.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:730125,731877}We finally did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:13.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731877,733671}We found more coal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:30.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748727,750062}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:45.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:764201,765744}Well done, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.74,0:12:50.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765744,770249}This means Lassie can\Ncome back to me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:51.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770249,771709}John?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:56.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:771709,776171}Now that we've done it,\NI feel sort of sleepy…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:13:00.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:776171,780634}I'm glad I trusted you, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.63,0:13:03.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780634,783846}I'm just… so very…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:06.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783846,786015}Sleepy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786015,787308}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:790978,792062}John.
Comment: 0,0:13:15.02,0:13:15.02,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:795024,795024}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.32,0:13:23.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:799320,803115}He can finally relax a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.74,0:13:28.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:805743,808370}We should let him sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.45,0:13:31.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809455,811498}Do we know anything\Nabout Lassie's whereabouts?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.49,0:13:35.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:811498,815669}We've received a message from Priscilla,\Nbut there was no news of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.66,0:13:37.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815669,817379}Figures.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.46,0:13:44.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823469,824803}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:52.68,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830726,832686}{\i1}Wait, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.90,0:13:58.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837900,838901}{\i1}Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.90,0:14:01.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:838901,841070}{\i1}From now on,\Nwe can always stay together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.44,0:14:05.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843447,845199}{\i1}No… That's not right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.19,0:14:09.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:845199,849286}{\i1}Lassie hasn't come\Nback home yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.32,0:14:12.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850329,852623}{\i1}I wonder where is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.45,0:14:16.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:853457,856960}{\i1}What kind of places\Nis she traveling to now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:21.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:860714,861590}{\i1}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.84,0:14:25.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:862841,865302}{\i1}Where did you go, Lassie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.68,0:14:31.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868680,871350}{\i1}Where are you now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.64,0:14:34.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:871642,874353}{\i1}When will I see you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882945,884196}{\i1}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:54.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893414,894706}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:00.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899711,900838}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:04.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:901171,904174}I'm so sorry I made you\Ngo through all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.80,0:15:11.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910806,911432}John?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.64,0:15:21.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920649,921942}Priscilla?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:25.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:923861,925279}Did you sleep well?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:29.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:925863,929450}They flew here\Nall the way from Scotland.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.15,0:15:31.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:930159,931994}They flew?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.99,0:15:33.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931994,933912}How long was I sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.91,0:15:35.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:933912,935247}Two days straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:36.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935247,936373}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:39.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:936373,939334}Was I really sleeping all that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:40.62,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939334,940627}John.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:43.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942212,943422}Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.42,0:15:44.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943422,944798}I'll be frank with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:50.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944798,950637}When I made that deal with you, I never\Nimagined you'd actually find a new deposit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:951847,953474}You have done an outstanding job.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:57.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:953474,957311}I am truly impressed by your victory\Nand bow my head to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.31,0:15:58.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957311,958520}However…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:01.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:959771,961148}I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.52,0:16:05.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961523,965277}I promised you that\NI would give Lassie back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:07.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965277,967946}But I am unable\Nto keep that promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.94,0:16:10.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:967946,970407}As you already know, Lassie has—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.40,0:16:12.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970407,972159}Right! Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:972159,973660}I have to go greet her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:18.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975621,978415}Lassie is still walking\Ntowards our town.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:19.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978415,979333}Ah…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:21.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979333,981585}I'm gonna change. Please get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:23.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981585,983295}– John!\N– What's gotten into you, John?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:27.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:985130,987007}Listen close, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:30.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987007,990719}If Lassie returns, it will be\Nnothing short of a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:31.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990719,991720}Grandfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:35.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:991720,995432}It had to be said. I am sorry, but I am not\Na man who beats around the bush.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.43,0:16:37.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:995432,997976}You're wrong.\NLassie is on her way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.97,0:16:39.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997976,999228}That's… uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:999228,1001480}I saw her! I saw her coming here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:42.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1001480,1002481}You saw her?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002481,1004608}But… Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.60,0:16:45.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004608,1005651}Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.65,0:16:46.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1005651,1006860}To the north side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.86,0:16:50.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006860,1010239}When Lassie left Scotland,\Nshe headed straight toward this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:05.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1024503,1025712}Hey, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.71,0:17:07.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1025712,1027005}Oh? Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.00,0:17:08.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1027005,1028090}To see Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.09,0:17:09.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028090,1029132}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029841,1031885}I'm going to greet Lassie.
